---
title: Peanut Butter Burger with Crispy Bacon and Oven Fries
description: Celebrate Father's Day with this nutty spin on a burger and fries! Warm peanut butter melts over top of the smoky bbq beef burgers, with onions and crispy, salty bacon completing this flavour blast.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burger-au-beurre-darachides-f2f7d2fe.jpg
